  "dct_description_sm": [
    "New York City Selected Facilities and Program Sites 2012 is a point theme representing public and private educational, recreational, public safety, health, mental health, substance abuse, mental retardation, day care, foster care, senior citizen and homeless facilities and programs throughout New York City. These facilities or programs are, with few exceptions, either operated, funded, licensed, or certified by a government agency. Attribute information includes the location, type, and capacity of each facility."
